To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private Stochastic _sto;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_sto = STO(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_sto.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "faststoch", _sto.FastStoch.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "stochk", _sto.StochK.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "stochd", _sto.StochD.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "stochastic", _sto.Current.Value);
}
